trending.title: Trending Now
trending.description: The movies and shows Tubi lovers are buzzing about right now.

283861.title: American High School
283861.description: The most popular girl in school is already married to her sweetheart and headed for divorce in her senior year at a not-so-normal high school.

300447.title: Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
300447.description: A widowed investor soups up an old racing car and discovers he has given it the ability to fly. He then takes his kids on an unforgettable adventure.

302157.title: Duel At Diablo
302157.description: A sweeping western tale about the conflict between the Apache and the white man as a cowboy travels with a family being pursued by the Apache.

302260.title: Things You Can Tell Just By Looking At Her
302260.description: Five interweaving vignettes following a group of women, over the course of a few days, as their lives become entangled, eroded, enriched and ultimately changed forever.

302263.title: Untamed Heart
302263.description: A waitress and a busboy start a whirlwind romance after he rescues her after work from an attack in this tale of two souls destined to be together.

302499.title: Soul Survivors
302499.description: Following a horrible car accident, a beautiful college freshman finds herself trapped in a twilight world somewhere between life and death.

302684.title: Asylum
302684.description: A college student discovers her dorm was once a notorious asylum where mental patients were tortured by their insane doctor. The students now living in the dormitory each have their own issues and troubles, and the murderous doctor who now haunts the dormitory seeks to "cure" them.

302686.title: Disturbing Behavior
302686.description: The new kid in town stumbles across something sinister about the town's method of transforming its unruly teens into upstanding citizens.

306920.title: Antitrust
306920.description: Milo has scored his dream job working for his idol but soon learns that the company may be less than scrupulous in how it conducts its business.

310126.title: College
310126.description: They're not in college yet, but three high school seniors unexpectedly find themselves with the wildest frat on their prospective school's campus.

310136.title: Hotel Rwanda
310136.description: The true story of a brave hotel manager who risked his and his family’s lives to harbor over 1,000 refugees during the 1994 Rwandan genocide.

337825.title: Afternoon Delight
337825.description: An unhappy housewife takes her husband to a strip club to spice things up but when she invites a stripper to be their nanny, their lives unravel.

348454.title: Pathology
348454.description: Upon graduating from medical school, Ted Gray joins a lauded pathology program — but he suspects his colleagues may be too comfortable with death.

348929.title: Altitude
348929.description: An FBI agent agrees to help a thief escape from a hijacked airplane, but soon finds out that his ex-partners are leading the deadly operation.

367667.title: Battle of Los Angeles
367667.description: With help from a WWII veteran, a Marine lieutenant fights to save Earth from an invasion when a UFO appears over Los Angeles in this sci-fi thriller.

367799.title: Paranormal Entity
367799.description: A paranormal investigator was framed for his sister's murder, but this discovered footage reveals the dark secret behind the young girl's death.

369861.title: The Prince
369861.description: A retired assassin is drawn back into the life he abandoned when he discovers his daughter has been kidnapped while away at school.

369865.title: Tracers
369865.description: Hoping to get out of debt to an organized crime gang, a bicycle messenger joins a group that uses parkour to pull of dangerous heists.

376067.title: The Curve
376067.description: Two college students are so desperate for a 4.0 that they kill their roommate and frame it as a suicide after they discover a new school policy.

376162.title: Girl Most Likely
376162.description: A failed playwright returns home to her eccentric mother and a house of full of oddballs in order to get her career, and her life, back on track.

382235.title: Sand Castles
382235.description: Noah and his rural Indiana family wrestle with the mysterious return of his now mute sister, who was kidnapped and held captive for over a decade.

385498.title: Arbitrage
385498.description: In this electrifying thriller, a hedge-fund magnate's fortunes turn when a deadly error threatens to destroy both his financial empire and his family.

389499.title: Picture This
389499.description: Mandy lands a date to the party of the year with her dream guy, Drew. But, she'll have to battle her overprotective dad and Drew's ex-girlfriend.

390869.title: Sweet Land
390869.description: Inge, a young German woman, travels to 1920's Minnesota to marry Olaf, a Norwiegan man. Her citizenship and the war with Germany create hardships.

405453.title: A Dog's Breakfast
405453.description: If you've never been good at anything in your life, why would murder be any different? A Dog's Breakfast is a head smacking, bone breaking, fiance bashing romp, about a family that just loves themselves to pieces. Patrick has always had a somewhat combative relationship with his little sister Marilyn. But when she brings home her new TV star fiance Ryan, it's all out war. When Patrick fails to drive a wedge between the happy couple, he reaches for sharper instruments. Every family has a few skeletons in the closet; A Dog's Breakfast is the nightmarishly funny mess Patrick makes when he tries to add another to his.

409833.title: Dark Moon Rising
409833.description: A group of shape-shifting werewolves on the brink of extinction descend upon a small town in search of a girl who is reborn once every 2000 years.

417558.title: The Babysitters
417558.description: A near-tryst with one of her clients inspires a savvy teen to turn her babysitting into a call-girl service, hooking married men up with her friends.

438043.title: Filth
438043.description: A scheming detective drowning in mad plots, drugs, alcohol and sexually abusive relationships becomes mentally unstable while working a murder case.

450461.title: A Girl Like Her
450461.description: A hidden camera documents the merciless bullying of 16-year-old Jessica by the most popular girl in school, and its tragic results.

451293.title: Operation Dunkirk
451293.description: A band of Allied soldiers battle their way through perilous Nazi territory to rescue a scientist with information that could turn the tide of the war.

451679.title: Assault on Wall Street
451679.description: When the economy crashes and causes a man to lose everything he has, including his loving wife, he seeks violent revenge for the life taken from him.

452481.title: The Imposter
452481.description: A documentary centered on a young man in Spain who claims to a grieving Texas family that he is their 16-year-old son who has been missing for 3 years.

456065.title: Rock 'N' Roll High School
456065.description: A group of rock-music-loving students, with help from The Ramones, take over their school to stand against its newly strict administration.

456282.title: Preservation
456282.description: A weekend in the woods becomes survival of the fittest for newlyweds Wit and Mike, and the husband's unhinged brother. But who is hunting who?

456859.title: Control
456859.description: A morally deviant inmate on death row agrees to be a test subject for a new behavior modification drug in order to get a second chance at life.

456913.title: U.S. Seals
456913.description: When modern pirates wage war on American ships, a crack team of soldiers are dispatched to destroy their base on an abandoned oil rig.

461854.title: One Last Thing
461854.description: A teenager with terminal cancer makes a last wish to spend the weekend with supermodel Nikki Sinclaire. With some friendly help, he just might get it.

462750.title: Nothing but the Truth
462750.description: In Washington, D.C., a reporter faces a possible jail sentence for outing a CIA agent, taking her case all the way to the Supreme Court.

465428.title: Gods of Egypt
465428.description: A mortal tries to save the world and his own true love by joining with a powerful god in an epic battle against his rival, the deadly god of darkness.

465655.title: The Life Before Her Eyes
465655.description: In this intense drama, two high school girls held captive by a gunman are forced to make the terrifying choice as to who will live and who will die.

466709.title: Heatstroke
466709.description: When a scientist is slain by an arms dealer, he leaves his girlfriend behind to protect his teenage daughter and face a grueling survival test.

466746.title: Smother
466746.description: A guy squirms under pressure when he gets fired and comes home to a wife,who is desperate to have a baby, and a suffocating mom, who is moving in.

468467.title: Futuresport
468467.description: Three people join forces to battle terrorism and save the country in what is the only athletic arena of the future, known as Futuresport.

469586.title: Hard Target
469586.description: The line between the hunted and the hunter becomes blurred when one man finds himself fighting a group that hunts other men for blood sport.

472717.title: Digging to China
472717.description: A lonely girl, who longs to escape her neglectful family and stultifying town, forges a bond with a mentally disabled man, which others aim to break.

473244.title: Falcon Rising
473244.description: After his sister is attacked by gangsters in Brazil, a dangerous man systematically stomps his way through thugs and crooks to get revenge.

478805.title: Black Moon Rising
478805.description: When the government hires a master thief to steal evidence stashed in a supercar, a smart auto thief swipes the auto, and a race against time begins.

485964.title: The Broken
485964.description: On a busy street in London, Gina thinks she sees herself drive past in her own car. Stunned, Gina follows the mystery woman to her apartment. Events take an eerie turn for the worse until Gina's awareness slides away from solid reality.

485992.title: ChromeSkull: Laid to Rest 2
485992.description: After his gruesome encounter with a girl, and being outmatched by his own assistant, ChromeSkull resurges with a horrifying massacre of his own.

486455.title: Wrong Side of Town
486455.description: A retired navy SEAL must rescue his kidnapped daughter from a former teammate bent on revenge, in this action thriller.

486556.title: A Home of Our Own
486556.description: Frances and her six children are looking for a fresh start. They spot an unfinished house and do whatever it takes to build a home of their own.

486887.title: Warriors of Virtue
486887.description: After a young boy enters a strange world, he meets five noble, wise and loyal Kung Foo kangaroos who teach him his own strengths as they fight evil.

488333.title: My Date With Drew
488333.description: An aspiring filmmaker with a lifelong crush on Drew Barrymore documents his quest to ask her on a date, before he must return his camera for a refund.

494921.title: Almost Adults
494921.description: In their last year of college, friends struggle to sustain their bond, as one’s emerging sexual identity and the other’s heartbreak pull them apart.

497277.title: Gracie's Choice
497277.description: When her drug-addicted, alcoholic, abusive mother is sent to jail, a teenage girl fights to be legally emancipated and raise her siblings on her own.

497888.title: Across the Hall
497888.description: Convinced that his fiancée is cheating on him, a man follows her to a seedy hotel, where his best friend comes to his aid to try to avert disaster.

500801.title: The Young Karl Marx
500801.description: At age 26, the exiled Karl Marx meets Friedrich Engels in turbulent 1844 Paris, and together the two brilliant rebels envision a new, more just world.

500900.title: High-Rise
500900.description: After a series of unsettling power outages occur in a posh London apartment tower, class and social standing become increasingly apparent.

501159.title: Shark Bait
501159.description: An aimless young fish, who has fallen head over gills in love, must find his destiny and save his home and dear ones from a big, bullying shark.

502473.title: Heroes Never Die
502473.description: Based on a true story, volunteer military soldiers become fierce heroes after they defend an airport under attack in the Ukraine by Russian troops.

505320.title: Kill Me Three Times
505320.description: A cunning assassin, who isn’t the only one trying to kill a surfing town temptress, gets entangled in three tales of murder, blackmail, and revenge.

505696.title: The Haunting of Molly Hartley
505696.description: A teen whose psychotic mother is sentenced to a mental ward tries to start a new life but is convinced that her soul has been sold to the devil.

507823.title: Lovesick
507823.description: A single and jaded school principal falls for a student’s aunt, triggering the clinical insanity and paranoia that happens every time he’s in love.

508834.title: Numb
508834.description: A cash-strapped couple discovers GPS coordinates that lead to stolen gold and partners with a pair of hitchhikers to enter a remote winter wilderness.

511167.title: The Right Kind of Wrong
511167.description: A failed writer becomes famous for being wrong in his ex-wife’s viral blog, then falls in love with a bride on the day of her wedding to another man.

512494.title: Side by Side
512494.description: Featuring interviews with famed directors like James Cameron, David Fincher and David Lynch, Keanu Reeves explores the future of digital cinema.

513560.title: Transpecos
513560.description: At a checkpoint on a desert highway, the lives of three border patrol agents are thrown into chaos when conducting what appears to be a routine stop.

515415.title: Satanic
515415.description: Four college students touring the Los Angeles true crime occult scene save a mysterious young woman, who may have dangerous motives.

516026.title: Man Vs.
516026.description: TV host Doug Woods is dropped off in the Canadian wilderness to survive one week alone. But he may not be the only one out there...

516366.title: Invasion U.S.A.
516366.description: A patriotic martial arts master comes out of retirement to wage battle against a legion of Soviet mercenaries who have invaded the United States.

520263.title: Laid to Rest
520263.description: A young girl with amnesia, found in a casket with a major head injury, recalls being attacked by a serial killer who’s still determined to kill her.

520271.title: The Possession of Michael King
520271.description: A widowed atheist, determined to disprove the existence of the supernatural, is consumed by a horrifying evil force that will not release him.

525069.title: The Mountain II
525069.description: After training in a covert special operations squad, two unlikely best friends begin their first mission to rescue an ISIS-captured reporter in Iraq.

531809.title: Vincent Price: El Último Hombre Sobre La Tierra (Soy Leyenda)
531809.description: Abrumado por la soledad a causa una pandemia a la que él es inmune y que acabó con la humanidad, un doctor tiene que combatir criaturas vampirezcas.

531847.title: Reaching for the Moon
531847.description: In 1950s Rio de Janeiro, Pulitzer Prize-winning American poet Elizabeth Bishop begins a tragic love affair with a successful female architect.

532395.title: La Pequeña Tienda De Los Horrores
532395.description: Una planta exótica en una floristería convence al manso aprendiz del tendero de recurrir a medidas espantosas para mantenerla viva y hacerla crecer.

532396.title: La Mansión De Los Horrores
532396.description: Un excéntrico millonario le otorgará diez mil dólares a quien sobreviva hasta el siguiente día el encierro en su espeluznante casa encantada.

532534.title: Sherlock Holmes Y El Arma Secreta
532534.description: Un científico suizo ha creado un arma que cambiaría el curso de la Segunda Guerra Mundial y Sherlock Holmes se ocupará de que no caiga en manos nazis.

532623.title: Vestida Para Matar
532623.description: Sherlock Holmes se propone descubrir qué esconde una atractiva mujer en tres cajitas de música y recuperar la última antes de que sea muy tarde.

532942.title: Zombie Hunter
532942.description: A tough man with an old Camero car full of liquor and guns has a bone to pick, especially while a street drug turns junkies into giant zombie mutants.

533526.title: Sherlock Holmes: La Mujer De Verde
533526.description: Las víctimas de una serie de asesinatos tienen en común un dedo cortado. Holmes sospecha de Moriarty, pero las pistas apuntan a una misteriosa mujer.

533563.title: Sherlock Holmes: Terror en La Noche
533563.description: A Holmes lo contratan para evitar el robo de un enorme diamante durante un viaje en tren. En el trayecto, hay un asesinato y la piedra desaparece.

536579.title: March of the Wooden Soldiers (In Color)
536579.description: Enter an enchanted fantasy world of timeless characters and magical moments where nothing goes right for a pair of bumbling toy makers.

537457.title: Blackway
537457.description: In the rugged Pacific Northwest, a grieving logger finds revenge and comes to the aid of a young woman, who is threatened by a sadistic crime lord.

539555.title: Mickey Virus
539555.description: A small-time hacker mistakenly commits a robbery when he helps the woman he loves reverse a transaction by hacking her company’s website.

543873.title: Desperado
543873.description: Stunning visuals highlight this action classic as a lone and mysterious gunman shoots through a border town to find his girlfriend’s killer.

543966.title: Dead & Buried
543966.description: A coastal town that seems to welcome strangers and tourists is actually killing them off and sending them back into society as happy, normal citizens.

544521.title: Hans Christian Andersen
544521.description: When a cobbler’s popular fairytales begin distracting the village school children, he moves to the city where a dancer inspires him to write a ballet.

550807.title: Camino a Bali (Doblado)
550807.description: Dos amigos desempleados de show-biz aceptan trabajos de búsqueda de tesoros en Bali para una princesa local y encuentran tesoros, amor y problemas.

552806.title: Abigail
552806.description: During an epidemic that forces a city into quarantine, a young woman goes on a quest to find her missing father and discovers she has magical powers.

555859.title: The Aggression Scale
555859.description: In this heart-racing thriller, a disturbed teen with a troubled past turns the tables on hitmen who have taken over his family’s home.

555940.title: Mr. Church
555940.description: A young mother and her daughter hire a talented and charismatic cook, which begins a fifteen year journey and a lasting family bond.

555993.title: El Hotel Del Terror (Doblado)
555993.description: Para investigar sobre brujería, una universitaria va a un tranquilo pueblo de Massachussetts y en su posada descubre un secreto sobre la gente de ahí.

555996.title: El Desvio (Doblado)
555996.description: La vida de Al Roberts, un pianista de Nueva York, se convierte en una pesadilla cuando decide hacer auto-stop para buscar a su novia que vive en Los Angeles

555997.title: El Autoestopista (Doblado)
555997.description: Dos pescadores recogen a un preso psicótico fugitivo que les dice que tiene la intención de asesinarlos cuando termine el viaje.

555998.title: Refugio Macabro (Doblado)
555998.description: El nuevo doctor entrevistará a los pacientes más peligrosos de un manicomio para determinar cuál de ellos es el ex psiquiatra de la institución.

556000.title: Bodas Reales (Doblado)
556000.description: Un acto de baile de hermano y hermana encuentra desafios y romance cuando se reserva en Londres durante la Boda Real.

557050.title: Drowning Mona
557050.description: A Sheriff investigating the murder of an upstate New York woman learns that her extremely hateful ways gave the whole town a motive to be rid of her.

560157.title: Noche Silenciosa Noche Sangrienta (Doblado)
560157.description: La mansión que heredó era antiguamente un manicomio y al investigar algunos delitos del pasado aterroriza a la gente de la región.

560161.title: CRAWLSPACE
560161.description: Gunther seems like a conscientious landlord who looks out for his female tenants. What they don't know is that he has a crawlspace from where he watches their every intimate move and plans their murders.

560398.title: Las Nieves Del Kilimanjaro (Doblado)
560398.description: El escritor Harry Street reflexiona sobre su vida mientras agoniza a causa de una infeccion durante un safari a la sombra del monte Kilamanjaro.

560399.title: La Noche De Los Muertos Vivientes (Doblado)
560399.description: Se atrincheraron en una antigua granja en Pensilvania creyendo que ahí estarán a salvo de la horda de zombies con sed de sangre que asola la zona.

563036.title: Bad Company
563036.description: When his identical twin brother is killed in the line of duty, a streetwise punk is recruited by a CIA agent to stop an arms deal from going bad.

567801.title: Dil
567801.description: The son of a poor man and the daughter of a proud rich man face the wrath of both sets of parents after they marry in spite of their disapproval.

570200.title: La Ultima Vez Que Vi Paris (Doblado)
570200.description: En el tumulto de la fiesta del fin de la guerra, una chica lo besa y desaparece; él la sigue, conoce a su futura esposa y empieza su vida en París.

570419.title: D.O.A. Con Las Horas Contadas (Doblado)
570419.description: A Frank Bigelow le acaban de decir  que ha sido envenenado y que solo le quedan unos dias de vida, ahora tiene de averiguar quien lo mato y por que.

571503.title: The Balibo Conspiracy
571503.description: After five Australian-based reporters disappear in East Timor, a journalist is approached by a young man to uncover the truth of what happened.

571579.title: United
571579.description: Inspiring account of the real-life tragedy of Manchester United’s football team, who lost eight athletes in a 1958 plane crash after a stunning win.

576504.title: El Asesino Del Taladro (Doblado)
576504.description: Los agobios cotidianos le taladraban tanto al enloquecido artista, que salió a desquitarse con los desamparados de las calles de Nueva York.

576524.title: Matar o no matar, éste es el problema (Doblado)
576524.description: Como su actuación en obras de Shakespeare no convenció para nada al círculo de críticos, un actor tiene una trágica venganza contra cada uno de ellos.

579626.title: Malone
579626.description: An ex-CIA agent trying to retire must help a small-town farmer and his daughter fight a conspiracy, led by a right-wing zealot and local millionaire.

581684.title: American Loser
581684.description: A young man plagued by challenges watches as his life falls apart before his eyes, until he meets a gold-digging woman who helps him get a grip.

583418.title: We Are Still Here
583418.description: Reeling from the death of their teen son, a couple starts over in a snowy New England town in an old house that they awaken from a century-old curse.

583435.title: The Innkeepers
583435.description: The last two employees of a century-old hotel in New England try to prove it’s truly haunted just as sinister guests start to check in and alarm them.

585796.title: Legend of the Fist: The Return of Chen Zhen (English Sub)
585796.description: Incredible martial arts sequences mark this thriller about a legendary fighter who takes on ruthless outside oppressors in World War II-era Shanghai.

587311.title: Momentum
587311.description: A secret black ops agent has her cover blown during a heist and ferociously fights her way out a conspiracy and the vicious scope of an assassin.

589375.title: Tango & Cash
589375.description: A pair of rival LAPD cops become unlikely allies when both are framed and imprisoned on drug charges that force them in cahoots to clear their names.

589926.title: Legend of the Fist (English Dub)
589926.description: Wild martial-arts sequences ricochet in this lush fable of 1920s China where a man becomes a one-man crime fighter against military and mafia enemies.

590476.title: The Hunger Games (LAS)
590476.description: En un futuro distópico, una joven de 16 años ofrece tomar el lugar de su hermana menor en una competencia en la que hay que luchar para salir vivo.

593662.title: The Heir Apparent: Largo Winch
593662.description: Following the murder of a billionare financer, his company desperately searches for his only heir, an adopted son who is pursued by assassins.

602057.title: The Official Story
602057.description: Después de terminada la Guerra Sucia en Argentina, una maestra se da a la tarea de averiguar quién es la madre de su hija adoptada.

602261.title: The Other Son
602261.description: When two young men, an Israeli Jew and a Palestinian, learn they were mistakenly switched at birth, complex repercussions impact both their families.

602963.title: El Inspector General (Doblado)
602963.description: A un estafador lo confunden con el enviado oficial del emperador Napoleon Bonaparte para combatir la corrupción generalizada que reina en Francia.

603123.title: Mysteries of Lisbon
603123.description: A whirlwind of adventure, revelations, violent passion, and love affairs, wrapped in a rhapsodic voyage from Europe to Brazil, forge an orphan’s fate

604274.title: Erased
604274.description: Ex-CIA operative Ben Logan (Aaron Eckhart, The Dark Knight) has been long estranged from his young daughter (Liana Liberato).

606512.title: Tyrannosaur
606512.description: Olivia Colman stars as a religious woman who is physically abused by her husband, and forms an unlikely friendship with an alcoholic man.

611668.title: Blood Feast
611668.description: A homicidal caterer plans to resurrect an Egyptian goddess using the body parts of young women as sacrifice and a lavish dinner party as the altar.

615657.title: El Chico De La Burbuja De Plástico (Doblado)
615657.description: El amor por su vecina hace que un adolescente nacido con deficiencias inmunitarias quiera salir de su burbuja libre de gérmenes.

616432.title: Contaminación Extraterrestre (Doblado)
616432.description: Un astronauta y un detective rastrean misteriosas esporas alienígenas hasta una plantación de café sudamericana controlada por clones extraterrestres.

616790.title: Metro
616790.description: Eddie Murphy teams with Michael Rapaport and Michael Wincott in this wildly entertaining, action-packed hit! Murphy plays Scott Roper, a fast-talking, wisecracking, on the edge hostage negotiator whose offbeat-but-winning style has made him San Francisco's top mediator! Roper will say...and do... absolutely anything to get his man. But when he comes face-to-face with a psychotic killer who's playing a lethal game of cat and mouse, he's finally met his match! Don't miss the excitement as the always amusing Murphy packs Metro with outrageous action that has critics and audiences cheering!

619642.title: Estranged
619642.description: After an accident leaves her confined to a wheelchair, a young woman is forced to return to her estranged family in an old estate full of dark secrets.

625736.title: The Pit
625736.description: When a solitary and strange adolescent boy makes a disturbing discovery in the depths of the forest, he wreaks vengeance on those who harass him.

631551.title: Dhol
631551.description: Four lazy best friends think they’ll get rich if one of them can get a wealthy young heiress to date them, but instead they land in a murder mystery.

631961.title: Blue Iguana
631961.description: Two low-level crooks get more than jet lag when a British lawyer hires them to steal a rare jewel that a trigger-happy gangster wants for himself.

631973.title: Hagazussa
631973.description: A psychedelic horror trip about a woman who discovers evidence of a 15th century woman whose tortured life spawned a supernatural curse on humanity.

639321.title: Wish Upon
639321.description: An old music box with the power of wish-granting creates a Monkey's Paw dilemma for a teenage girl whose loved ones begin to die violent deaths.

640311.title: Al Servicio De Las Damas (Doblado)
640311.description: Una señorita de la crema y nata de la sociedad contrata al vagabundo que se encontró en el basurero municipal como mayordomo de su excéntrica familia.

640613.title: El Extraño Amor De Martha Ivers (Doblado)
640613.description: Un hombre se reencuentra con una amiga de la infancia y su esposo, quienes creen conocer la verdad sobre la muerte de la tía rica de ella años antes.

640636.title: El Hombre Del Brazo De Oro (Doblado)
640636.description: Un músico tiene el firme propósito de rehacer su vida, pero deberá enfrentarse a su verdadero yo para dejar su adicción a las drogas.

640663.title: Ha Nacido Una Estrella (Doblado)
640663.description: Una joven llega a Hollywood con sueños de estrellato y solo los logra con la ayuda de un protagonista alcohólico cuyos mejores días han quedado atrás.

640664.title: Jack Y Los Frijoles Magicos (Doblado)
640664.description: Jack consigue chamba como niñero y, para dormir a su travieso cliente, le lee el clásico cuento de hadas del chico que vende la vaca de la familia.

640668.title: La Burla Del Diablo (Doblado)
640668.description: Un grupo de sinvergüenzas se dirige a África para hacerse rico cuando se topan con una pareja británica de aspecto inocente y su suerte cambia.

640894.title: Chameleon
640894.description: Two ex-convicts prey on gullible Los Angeles trophy wives and their rich old husbands until one of their marks upsets their plans with her own scam.

641581.title: Somewhere in Time
641581.description: A playwright visiting a hotel falls in love with an actress pictured in a 1912 photo and uses self-hypnosis to go 68 years back in time to meet her.

646635.title: Dogs
